{"tid":2479175,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國新型無人機Valkyrie 成功喺空中放出另一部無人機","createTime":"2021-04-07T15:27:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T19:18:44.000Z","uid":48083,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b235c8e8cc7f859e2c6d26d15d747bbfdc917062","tid":2479175,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:27:42.000Z","msg":"Drone-Ception: Valkyrie Drone Launches Mini-Drone in New Air Force Test<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nThe Air Force just demonstrated the ability to launch a drone from another drone, a step forward in complex aerial warfare without a human pilot.<br />\n<br />\nThe XQ-58A Valkyrie successfully released a small unmanned aerial vehicle from its internal weapons bay at the Yuma Proving Ground in Arizona on March 26, according to a service release. The test was conducted by the Air Force Research Laboratory and the Valkyrie's maker, Kratos Defense.<br />\n<br />\nThe launched drone was the ALTIUS-600, a small, cylindrical UAV made by Area-I, the release states.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.military.com/daily-news/2021/04/07/drone-ception-valkyrie-drone-launches-mini-drone-new-air-force-test.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.military.com%2Fdaily-news%2F2021%2F04%2F07%2Fdrone-ception-valkyrie-drone-launches-mini-drone-new-air-force-test.html&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYRUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=411516d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.military.com/daily-news/2021/04/07/drone-ception-valkyrie-drone-launches-mini-drone-new-air-force-test.html</a>"},{"pid":"5176cb3215bc8bd572c18e8912d2375928e5e130","tid":2479175,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:28:55.000Z","msg":"美國空軍5日宣佈，研發中的XQ-58A「女武神」無人機(Valkyrie)成功釋放了1枚體積更小的無人機，完成「無人機釋放無人機」的特殊實驗，此消息令中共震驚，直呼需「警惕」。<br />\n<br />\n4月5日，美國國防新聞週刊(Defense News)報導說，一架XQ-58A「女武神」無人機於3月26日進行了試驗，在亞利桑那州美軍尤馬試驗場上空飛行時，打開彈艙，投放了一架ALTIUS-600小型無人機。<br />\n<br />\n據稱，這是「女武神」無人機第6次在尤馬試驗場進行飛行試驗，並且首次在試驗飛行中打開彈艙，投放了一架筒狀發射器中攜帶的ALTIUS-600無人機。<br />\n<br />\nALTIUS-600無人機總重12.2公斤，飛行續航力可達4小時，除飛行裝備外，可加掛2.7公斤的載荷，包括攝像機、小型信號情報系統甚至殺傷彈頭。<br />\n<br />\nALTIUS-600也可以在不同軍種的多款載台上發射（先前曾由陸軍黑鷹直升機發射），執行反無人機、電子戰、信號情報監視和與情監偵任務。<br />\n<br />\n該消息引起中共黨媒關注，撰文直呼要「警惕」，中共軍事專家更稱「使用廉價無人機，發射更為便宜的微型無人機的技術，一旦成熟並廣泛應用於戰場，可能將對未來戰爭形態帶來重要變革」。<br />\n<br />\n20210407075236625.jpgALTIUS-600無人機發射後，各翼面與推進螺旋槳會自動展開，開始飛行執行任務。（取自美國國防部網站）<br />\n<br />\nALTIUS-600迷你無人機是由Area-I公司所設計製造的小型管式發射自動無人機，機翼在發射前可以收折，投放出去後才會伸展。<br />\n<br />\nXQ-58A「女武神」無人機，則是由克拉托斯（Kratos）公司與美空軍合作研發的無人機，具低成本、可損耗特性，2019年3月實現首飛，目前已被「空軍研究實驗室」（AFRL）納入「空中博格」（Skyborg）計劃選項，借此打造能控制無人機進行自主飛行、起降，並協助飛行員作戰的人工智能（AI）系統。<br />\n<br />\n美國空軍表示，XQ-58A被列為「可耗損」(attritable)的裝備，在軍方的定義是，「可重復使用的設備，但價格便宜，能夠承受一定的戰鬥損失」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bannednews.org/2021/04/blog-post_38.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannednews.org%2F2021%2F04%2Fblog-post_38.html&d=kuRIuFMgKSvsW5TefiiiYRUAsmJrpgm%2FsQZzOZZuI0I%3D&h=48157938\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bannednews.org/2021/04/blog-post_38.html</a>"},{"pid":"bdaf999acae4a11382a63bed2e5f3e0cbdd207a8","tid":2479175,"uid":51436,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T15:32:21.000Z","msg":"呢幾日強國一定又拎部黑煙玩具船出黎打飛機抗衡美帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3ceadc0949ea4f54decc572fff686986b5bcb4","tid":2479175,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"咩呀falcon呀？"},{"pid":"35db3bd7dfa11920a93ab6307786a5c9e215ecab","tid":2479175,"uid":19217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"有乜特別"},{"pid":"58b82ccb933d53980487c28aef90d3e66046fa42","tid":2479175,"uid":4526,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T16:24:53.000Z","msg":"誠懇呼籲唔好再討論美國無人機，你唔係美國人又搞佢哋架飛機，美國人會好反感"},{"pid":"acf6becbb9a38cd047b88ae756729e0fcd6977a4","tid":2479175,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58b82ccb